# Next.js Frontend

- App Router in `src/app/`; default to Server Components
- Add `'use client'` only for interactivity (forms, modals, filters)
- API calls via `src/lib/api/client.ts` (axios + `withCredentials: true`)
- Server data fetching: TanStack Query in client components or fetch in RSC
- Validate forms with Zod + react-hook-form
- Types live in `src/types/` — mirror API resource shapes

```tsx
// ✅ Client component for interactive filter
'use client';
export function FilterSidebar() { ... }

// ✅ Server page wrapping client grid
export default async function HomePage() { return <BrowsePage />; }
```
